5. Hobby:reading is to the right of Hobby:collecting
6. Cigar:old-gold == Movie-Genre:zombie
7. Cigar:kools == Hobby:card-games
8. Sport:snowboarding is in the middle
9. Transport:skateboard is on the far left
10. Cigar:chesterfields is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:adventure
11. Cigar:kools is to the left or right of Movie-Genre:animation
12. Cigar:lucky-strike == Sport:swimming
13. Transport:roller == Cigar:parliaments
14. Transport:skateboard is to the left or right of Hobby:dancing

